thread.title: Jing
thread.title_full: PACK & SEND Australia reviewed by Jing

author: Jing
title: Jing
text: The website is easy to use, very user friendly. Also, the consultant at the shop front was very nice, helpful and accommodating to me. I had a few questions to ask and she was able to give me confidence in posting internationally with them - it was my first time and I was a bit nervous about whether the parcel was going to get to it's destination.
